      <h2 class="govuk-heading-m">Our introductory message</h2>
      <p class="govuk-body">You may see a pop-up welcome message when you first visit GOV.UK&nbsp;Pay. We’ll store a cookie so that your computer knows you’ve seen it and knows not to show it again.</p>
